The Trial Source Toolbox 2.0The Trial Source Toolbox requires MATLAB, version 5.0 or later.  To use the toolbox, put the folders 'Trial Source' and 'Trial Source:Extras' on your MATLAB path.To use the 'pquest' trial source, you need the Psychophysics Toolbox (available from http://color.psych.ucsb.edu/psychtoolbox/).Adobe PDF documentation is included in the file TrialSourceToolbox.pdf.Richard MurrayDepartment of PsychologyUniversity of Torontorichard@psych.utoronto.cawww.psych.utoronto.ca/~richardOctober 1, 1999